<p>
<note n="0497001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0497001">不喜樂＋（害）【三】【宮】，不喜樂＝害【聖】</note>
<note n="0497002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0497002">用＝德【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0497003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0497003">光＝先【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0497004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0497004">止＝上【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0497005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0497005">入＝又【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0498001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0498001">多＝名【宮】</note>
<note n="0498002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0498002">星＝華【明】</note>
